    "Main contributions of the 34 articles included in the review",
    "All routine tasks that occupy the teacher's time can be addressed by the chatbot, freeing up the teacher to attend to more important actions related to the learning context and the student's personality.",
    "According to Villarroel (2021), GPT-3 makes it possible to quickly diagnose the weaknesses of each student, without the need for the teacher to review a large quantity of questionnaires and tasks, giving them more time for individualized tasks that are aimed at sets of specific skills.",
    "AI can be used for automatic learning in which each student is specifically tracked, producing detailed progress reports that specify their comprehension of the different skills being evaluated.",
    "The teacher's work thus becomes the personalizing of learning programs according to the strengths and weaknesses of each student."
  ],
